Colors

INSTRUCTIONS: Using the website from the lecture (http://html-color-codes.info/) update the styling for the paragraphs to the appropriate colour, using HTML colour codes.

<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
    	<title>Colors</title>
        <style type="text/css">   
			#black {
            	
            }
			#white {
            	
            }
        </style>
        </head>
    <body>
    	<div id="background">
    		<p id="black">This is a paragraph</p>
        	<p id="white">This is another paragraph!</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>


Answer:
<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
    	<title>Colors</title>
        <style type="text/css">   
			#black {
            	color:#000000
            }
			#white {
            	color:#FFFFFF
            }
        </style>
        </head>
    <body>
    	<div id="background">
    		<p id="black">This is a paragraph</p>
        	<p id="white">This is another paragraph!</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>